data.description: Searching for a Nexthome that checks all of your boxes? Look no further than 2757 American Avenue. Spacious, brick ranch featuring covered front porch, luxury vinyl plank flooring, fresh paint, upgraded kitchen with all major appliances including a new stainless steel french door refrigerator and built in oven, granite counter tops, tiled back splash, coffee bar and custom pantry system, In-law suite addition with private entry, Florida room over looking a fully fenced backyard with outdoor entertaining space including a covered picnic area, grilling station and storage shed which could easily be converted into an epic she shed/man cave. Back inside you'll be impressed by ample sized bedrooms, numerous living areas including a formal living, dining, and great room featuring vaulted ceilings with beveled, exposed beams. New roof 2021, NO HOA, zoned for Lexington One schools. Easy access to CAE airport, downtown Columbia, Lexington, and major interstates! Make those appointments to view today!
